<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ReserveAqui Hotel</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* Paleta de Cores */
        :root {
            --primary-color: #99b898; /* Verde suave */
            --secondary-color: #fecea8; /* Bege claro */
            --accent-color: #2a363b; /* Azul escuro */
            --highlight-color: #e84a5f; /* Vermelho coral */
            --background-color: #ff847c; /* Laranja claro */
            --white: #ffffff; /* Branco */
        }

        /* Estilos Globais */
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        /* Navbar */
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: var(--accent-color);
            color: var(--white);
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .navbar .brand {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--white);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .navbar ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .navbar ul li a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--white);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .navbar ul li a:hover {
            color: var(--highlight-color);
        }

        .navbar .booking-button {
            background-color: var(--highlight-color);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .navbar .booking-button:hover {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero-section {
            background-color: var(--white); /* Fundo branco */
            height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .hero-section h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .hero-section p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .hero-section .cta-button {
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: var(--highlight-color);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .hero-section .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }

        /* Seção de Benefícios */
        .benefits {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
        }

        .benefit-item {
            flex: 1 1 200px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .benefit-item i {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--highlight-color);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .benefit-item h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: var(--accent-color); /* Mantém o azul escuro */
        }

        .benefit-item p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #333; /* Cor escura para o texto */
        }

        .benefit-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--accent-color);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }

            .hero-section h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .hero-section p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .benefits {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section">
        <h1>ReserveAqui Hotel</h1>
        <p>Um lugar tranquilo para se hospedar</p>
        <a href="@Url.Action("ViewHotelHospede", "Hotels")" class="cta-button">Explorar Quartos</a>
    </section>

    <!-- Seção de Benefícios -->
    <section class="benefits">
        <div class="benefit-item">
            <i class="fas fa-wifi"></i>
            <h3>Wi-Fi Gratuito</h3>
            <p>Conexão rápida e gratuita em todos os ambientes do hotel.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-item">
            <i class="fas fa-utensils"></i>
            <h3>Café da Manhã Incluso</h3>
            <p>Desfrute de um café da manhã completo e variado todos os dias.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-item">
            <i class="fas fa-spa"></i>
            <h3>Spa e Academia</h3>
            <p>Relaxe no spa e mantenha sua rotina de exercícios em nossa academia.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-item">
            <i class="fas fa-swimming-pool"></i>
            <h3>Piscina</h3>
            <p>Uma bela piscina para momentos de lazer e diversão.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
